    "description": {
      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <a title=\"PZO1121\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/1601253907/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=1601253907&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=httpwwwd20pfs-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PZO1121</a></p>\r\n<p>When this unguent-prepared with vile alchemical reagents and the gore of fiends-is applied to a wounded <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-listings/outsiders/tiefling\">tiefling</a> or evil <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Outsider\">outsider</a> (not currently at maximum <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Hit-Points\">hit points</a>), it momentarily transforms the essence of the target into something even more fearsome and demonic. While under the effects of a fiendgore unguent, a <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-listings/outsiders/tiefling\">tiefling</a> or an evil <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Outsider\">outsider</a> gains a +2 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Circumstance-Bonus\">circumstance bonus</a> on <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/intimidate\">Intimidate</a> checks and a +1 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Circumstance-Bonus\">circumstance bonus</a> to the DC of all spells with the fear descriptor that they cast. Applying the unguent is a delicate process, requiring a <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Full-Round-Actions\">full-round action</a>, and can only be properly applied to a willing or <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/conditions#TOC-Helpless\">helpless</a> creature. If applied to a creature other than a <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-listings/outsiders/tiefling\">tiefling</a> or an evil <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Outsider\">outsider</a>, it sickens the creature instead. The unguent's effects (either beneficial or harmful) last for 1 minute.</p>\r\n",
